# Etapa 20 — Activity logs

## Objetivo
Registro homogéneo de eventos relevantes del sistema con actor, acción,
entidad afectada y contexto before/after. Implementado via Observers de Laravel.

---

## Estructura del log

```json
{
  "actor_user_id": 42,
  "action": "workspace.created",
  "subject_type": "Workspace",
  "subject_id": 87,
  "workspace_id": 87,
  "enterprise_id": 5,
  "room_id": null,
  "metadata_json": {
    "before": null,
    "after": { "name": "Mi workspace", "status": "active" },
    "context": { "parent_workspace_id": null },
    "reason": null
  },
  "ip_address": "192.168.1.1",
  "user_agent": "Mozilla/5.0..."
}
```

---

## Acciones a registrar

| Acción | Entidad | Before/After |
|---|---|---|
| `user.registered` | User | null / user data |
| `user.login` | User | null / null |
| `user.deleted` | User | user data / null |
| `enterprise.created` | Enterprise | null / enterprise data |
| `enterprise.member_invited` | Invitation | null / invitation data |
| `enterprise.member_joined` | EnterpriseUser | null / member data |
| `enterprise.member_removed` | EnterpriseUser | member data / null |
| `subscription.changed` | Subscription | before / after |
| `workspace.created` | Workspace | null / workspace data |
| `workspace.updated` | Workspace | before / after |
| `workspace.deleted` | Workspace | workspace data / null |
| `workspace.member_added` | WorkspaceUser | null / member data |
| `asset.created` | Asset | null / asset data |
| `asset.trashed` | Asset | asset data / null |
| `room.created` | Room | null / room data |
| `room.ended` | Room | before / after |
| `room.participant_joined` | RoomParticipant | null / participant data |
| `room.participant_kicked` | RoomParticipant | participant data / null |
| `stream.started` | Stream | before / after |
| `stream.ended` | Stream | before / after |

